<title>USA: Redman schedules merger vote on Oct. 24.</title>
<headline>Redman schedules merger vote on Oct. 24.</headline>
<dateline>DALLAS 1996-09-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>Redman Industries Inc said Monday it has set Oct. 24 as the date for a special meeting of stockholders to vote on its proposed merger with Champion Enterprises.</p>
<p>At the meeting, shareholders of record as of September 23 will be asked to approve the merger, in which each Redman common share would be converted into 1.24 Champion common shares.</p>
